"content": "<h2>Mist is a natural phenomenon</h2>\n<h3>Mist as a source of water</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:5-Gen2:6\">GEN 2:5–2:6</a> <em>NIV footnote at verse 6</em></p>\n<h3>Mist as a barrier to effective vision</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:11\">ACT 13:11</a></p>\n<h2>Mist as a symbol</h2>\n<h3>Of a lack of substance or permanence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:4\">HOS 6:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:14\">JAS 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:3\">HOS 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17\">2PE 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Of God's forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:22\">ISA 44:22</a></strong></p>",
